DOCUMENTATION


Purpose of software

This software serves the process of performing retail store operations. This system serves to replace any traditional system of pen and paper. Here are further advantages to using a software like this:
•	It is fast
•	Less time consuming.
•	Avoids error that could have been caused by humans
•	It’s a lot more accurate.



How is this software build?

It consist different modules such as Stock,Employees,Payroll,Manager
This modules work in conjunction with each other as relationships.
This different modules all contain functions that helped reduce the problem in a simplified way because each part can be translated to pseudo code block by block.
The functions were then translated into pseudo code in which they will be interpreted further into a full software application.





The data related to this project is stored in the same directory/repository




